Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan ini, sudah 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurang 100 lagi\Ndemi mendoakan kemenangan Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Santai sekali dia meneleponku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, ini Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf mendadak,\Nbesok siang kau ada waktu luang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuterima pekerjaan sebanyak mungkin\Ndemi memuja Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada permintaan bersih-bersih.\NKuserahkan padamu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata si gorila ini, Ouri Sakaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku jadi center,\Ndatanglah ke rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemenangnya belum ditentukan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikap macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini klien.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu alasanku\Nmemintamu datang kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, tempat ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rumah orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa terbiasa\Ntinggal di apartemen kumuh dan sempit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau pacaran dengan pria itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dan Tamon pacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin Tamon puas\Ndengan satu wanita saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pria yang kelak akan menjadikan\Nseluruh umat manusia pacarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau berani meremehkannya lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuhancurkan kau karena\Ntak menghormati Dewa. Paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan keluarkan aura aneh begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah jika tidak. Itu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memintaku kemari cuma untuk tanya itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kerjai aku begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panas sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, jangan asal tempel koyok padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada lima babak\Ndalam Pertarungan Posisi Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Babak kedua sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon dan Ouri seri di posisi pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Situasinya masih belum jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sudah kusuruh pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,\Nmendadak ada insiden perawatan pasien.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan bukan prasangkaku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana bisa aku pulang\Nkalau kau pingsan di depanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau pikir Tuan Suram dan aku\Npunya hubungan istimewa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kau memintaku datang\Nuntuk memastikannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak punya pilihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada cara lain untuk menghubungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun alasannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena aku di sini untuk kerja,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuselesaikan semua\Npekerjaan rumah dalam jam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa? Kau tidak membenciku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ini pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, besok kau juga harus datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong buat janji lewat telepon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, semoga lekas sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumahnya besar sekali.\NMembersihkannya melelahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya aku harus ke rumah Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku merasa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terakhir kali aku melihat Tuan Suram\Nsaat festival musim panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu, aku melihat\Nbanyak sisi tersembunyinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikihara pasti tak sengaja muncul saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba aku merasa hampir mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia masih sama seperti biasanya.\NSyukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Kinoshita, kau pergi ke rumah Ouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Bagaimana kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia khusus memberi tahu Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga pesan jasa pembersih untuk besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku akan ke sana lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Ouri sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau tidak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak ikut latihan hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hanya bilang akan cuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin tak mau orang lain\Nmelihat sisi lemahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia seperti hewan liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah dia baik-baik saja atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuanya di luar negeri.\NMereka tidak di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku juga akan ke sana besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram, kau lakukan saja tugasmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suhu tubuhmu lebih tinggi dari kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram juga mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sebut orang itu di depanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Tamon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri pasti sangat tertekan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dalam Pertarungan Posisi Center ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisakah mereka berdua akur?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang menjenguk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau suka manis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku tak tahu harus beli apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak butuh.\NTidak lucu sama sekali. Pulang sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku akan kembali jadi tanah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cuma takut memilih hal yang salah\Ndan kau akan memarahinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya kau tak pernah mendekatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau kemari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak pernah bolos latihan karena sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku agak khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau di sini untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak kau lakukan\Npekerjaan rumah untukku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau kau benar-benar di sini untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah membersihkan wastu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi baru kali ini\Nlihat rumah dengan kolam renang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga kali pertamaku. Mengejutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pendapatmu tentang Sakaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri membenciku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu bisa dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu itu, aku ke Tokyo sendirian\Nuntuk audisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak kenal siapa pun dan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri mengajariku banyak hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempatnya di sebelah sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menjadikanmu kacungku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada pertanyaan, tanya saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nomor satu, Tamon Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi aku selalu berpikir,\Napa pun yang dia katakan, akan kuterima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Ouri bisa menjadi center,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku juga harus mundur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku berubah pikiran belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa ada cara lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat dengar Ouri sakit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku berpikir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh tak mau bersaing dengan Ouri\Nsaat dia tak bisa berusaha maksimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa kini aku mengerti
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa Ouri tidak menyukaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kali ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak akan mengalah padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malaikat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua bicara apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat bersihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cepatlah sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berusaha keras\Nuntuk mengalahkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya kau berkata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, akan kuhancurkan kau selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah abu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku… Aku tak akan jadi abu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sombong sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku setahun lebih tua darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada masalah, Berandal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus lebih banyak istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Jangan memerintahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan kabur. Kau kacungku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak pernah bilang mau jadi kacungmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa? Bukankah kau setuju saat itu?\N- Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- pertarungan mereka berlanjut.\N- Jangan… Jangan siram aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemenang babak ketiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan Posisi Center\Nadalah Ouri Sakaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kategori babak keempat adalah Aksi Rahasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menghargai setiap gelas\Nseolah itu penggemarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhasil melindungi kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemenangnya adalah Tamon Fukuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon saat ini di posisi pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat peringkat berubah,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pertarungan sorakan penggemar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga memanas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, mari kita mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami berusaha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meniru tarian Tamon dengan sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan terakhir
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- adalah bernyanyi.\N- Itu F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lagi pula, ini babak final.\N- Aku penasaran siapa yang akan menjadi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ini murni adu bakat.\N- center.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasil Pertarungan Posisi Center F/ACE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan segera terungkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini akan disiarkan langsung
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di lokasi Festival Musim Panas Nstation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih lagi untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama. Aku permisi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak dia bicara dengan Ouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa dia sudah melupakan banyak hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisinya juga baik. Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia melupakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah merawatku waktu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kau sudah sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menonton babak ketiga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menang dengan indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon juga menang di babak keempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Babak terakhir adalah kompetisi menyanyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan menyusul\Ndan jadi juara pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau bersaing dengan Ouri\Nsaat dia tak bisa maksimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nlakukan yang terbaik sampai akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihatmu berusaha keras,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon pasti juga akan bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati jangan sampai sakit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku batalkan kesepakatan kita sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sebagai gantinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika aku menang,\Nkau harus jadi penggemarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika Tamon menang,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadilah penggemar Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang mau? Akan kubuang itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}RAIN - Hujan turun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku hanya perlu\Nberlatih sedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bekerja keras, tapi jangan berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram yang selalu gelisah,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidur santai di depan orang lain.\NAda apa sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bulu matanya sangat lentik\Nbisa untuk tempat istirahat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan pipinya semulus perosotan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hidup di dimensi yang sama,\Nkenapa resolusi dia jauh lebih tinggi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun yang berdiri di samping Tamon\Nterasa seperti makhluk resolusi rendah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia lahir di dunia berbeda,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin sudah dihukum mati\Nkarena pelecehan kecantikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Cleopatra bereinkarnasi\Nsebagai pria tampan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin akan terlihat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia tampak lebih pucat\Ndaripada biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, lakukan yang terbaik\Nsampai akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakan sesuatu yang berat\Nmenekan punggungku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan Tamon, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti itu\Nhanya bisa terjadi dalam mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kata nenek dalam imajinasiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Apa aku terlalu berkhayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan cuma halusinasi dan fantasi,\Ntapi juga sentuhan semu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa karena aku terlalu bersemangat\Nlihat wajah tidur biasku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, Tamon bekerja sangat keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana bisa aku melamun di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage, fokuslah pada pekerjaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besok akhirnya pertarungan terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua akan ditentukan saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga kerja keras Tamon membuahkan hasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa pertarungan fisik konyol itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku juga punya kesempatan untuk menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah memikirkan materi\Nkompetisi kuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu pesimis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah pertarungan hari ini\Nakan menambah poin sesuai peringkat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada kesempatan membalikkan keadaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus sekali.\NMudah bicara bagi posisi kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Selamat pagi, Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa? Kau jarang terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat… pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaramu serak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, semua akan menampilkan\Nlagu baru "RAIN".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kalian sudah banyak berlatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berusahalah maksimal\Ndan jangan sampai menyesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ayo, Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Babak final Pertarungan Posisi Center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}resmi dimulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang diharapkan dari Tamon.\NDia pasti menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak seperti babak pertama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kali ini dia sampaikan\Nnuansa lagu perpisahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sekilas,\N- Dia berusaha menahan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- dia tampak sengaja menahan\N- auranya yang bersinar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia belum pernah pakai\N- auranya yang bersinar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi bagiku,\N- gaya menyanyi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- sepertinya kondisinya tak baik.\N- Ini sisi baru Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Sebagai penggemar,\Naku harus memercayai Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelima episode spesial telah ditayangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kukatakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami akan tampilkan lagu baru\NBeberapa hari lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di Festival Musim Panas Nstation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Latihlah lagu itu sesuai pembagian lirik\Nyang baru saja kukirimkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ouri, Tamon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa wajah kalian menyedihkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski bisa menipu penonton,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian tak bisa menipuku dan juri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah kalian yang bersaing\Ndemi posisi dua teratas di acara bakat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka yang diam-diam berlatih\Ndan memaksakan diri
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak pantas disebut profesional.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ingin jadi megabintang dunia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian harus bisa tampil 2.000 persen\Nsetiap saat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}F/ACE tidak butuh\Norang yang tidak sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak suvenir penggemar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau yang merah muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, kita harus beli ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin kulihat,\Nmakin aku merasa kondisinya tidak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika Tamon\Ntidak mendapatkan posisi center?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana perasaan Tuan Suram sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia tertekan karena terlalu sering\Nmencari dirinya di internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia makan selain mi instan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia tidur nyenyak di ranjangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo buat spanduk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini kita bisa membawanya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore! Omong-omong…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia akan menangis lagi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena terlalu banyak berpikir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum jumpa Tuan Suram,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak mencemaskan Tamon seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku benar-benar penggemar\Nyang tak memenuhi syarat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau selalu mengikuti jadwal\Ndan tak pernah mengeluh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa memperpanjang latihanmu\Ndan gali kubur sendiri di saat begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau bodoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau juga tak tampil\Nbaik kali ini, paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tipe orang\Nyang mengacau di saat genting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berusaha terlalu keras kali ini,\Ndan semuanya sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya ini salahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, ada apa denganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat senang\Nlebih banyak orang yang mendukungku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi di saat bersamaan,\Naku makin tak mau gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau mengecewakan penggemarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya aneh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin baik mereka padaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku makin bahagia dan takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berpikir,\N"Bagaimana jika mereka meninggalkanku?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu aku makin takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar jika orang-orang pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pasti ada penggemar berat juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada gunanya memikirkan\Nhal yang sudah jelas, paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak memahamimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa memahaminya secara rasional,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mungkin\Naku masih belum bisa merelakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menerima banyak dukungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebenarnya kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai kapan kau akan terpengaruh\Noleh kegagalan masa lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang di sini untuk F/ACE, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasilnya akhirnya keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan Posisi Center\Nyang dinantikan telah berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, anggota yang akan menjadi center\Nakan terungkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ayo, Tamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka melihat Tamon bersinar\Ndi panggung,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memberi kami mimpi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan fantasi yang tak realistis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu juga karena Tamon asli\Nbekerja keras di balik layar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya, F/ACE akan menampilkan "RAIN".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan rintik hujan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membasahi bahuku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hingga aku lupa\N- Bagus, Keito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bahwa payungku\N- Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tertinggal entah di mana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, terang menyinari kehampaanku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kesepian lelehkan kebencianku\N- Dia mengkhawatirkan hal sepele.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Saat aku bertemu denganmu\N- Terkadang dia gagal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- dan sering menangis.\N- Dan saat kita basah kuyup karena hujan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi dia tak pernah kabur.\N- Tamon tidak menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ini bohong. Katakan ini mustahil!\N- Begitu aku tahu ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujan yang kukenal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa sedingin ini?\N- Aku tak akan pernah bisa kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru menyadarinya sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}RAIN mulai turun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membasuh semuanya
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak kusadari saat itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Langit pagi tanpamu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cerah tanpa kusadari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}RAIN tak akan berhenti
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di bawah langit, aku mulai berlari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini awal yang baru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari-hariku bersamamu Kusimpan dalam hati
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kini kuambil langkah baru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Telah menemaniku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}RAIN - Hujan turun
